    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/DashboardView.tsx` to handle the primary Dashboard workspace:\n- Friendly grit-filled heading: \"Ready to Grind?\" paired with the current local day of week.\n- Real-time weekly stats metrics panel: active sessions count, total completed sets, and average workout completion percentage.\n- Today\'s workout exercise deck with interactive set tracker dots (saving states in localStorage).\n- Fast clicking access: Tapping any exercise launches the video/tips detail slider sheet.\n- Integrated `AIChat` box directly embedded at the front of the screen."
