  planner_response {
    modified_response: "\n\nI have built **Fitness World**, the full-stack, AI-powered personal training and workout tracking application using **React (Vite) + Node.js (Express) + Google GenAI SDK**.\n\n### \360\237\214\237 Visual Identity & Aesthetic Principles\n- **Dark Cosmic Slate Theme**: The application operates on an eye-safe black background (`#070707`) with custom slate gray containers (`#141414`) and high-contrast crimson red highlights (`#E24B4A`) to mimic an authentic, high-power fitness workout space.\n- **Premium Font Pairings**: Utilizes headlining **Bebas Neue** for dramatic typography displays, synced with highly scannable **Barlow** sans-serif font weights for body labels and metrics cards.\n- **Fluid Layout Transitions**: Configured standard mobile-first bottom menus that dock to side navigation rails on desktop screens.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\233\241\357\270\217 Core Features Built\n\n1. **Intense Landing Experience (`/`)**\n   - High-contrast visual introducing the gym tagline *\"YOUR AI-POWERED PERSONAL TRAINER\"*.\n   - Prominent call-to-actions supporting fast transitions to *Start Training* or *View Programs*.\n   - Bento-grid highlights detailing *AI Coaching*, *Video Guides*, and *Trackers*.\n\n2. **Grit-Driven Workspace Dashboard (`/dashboard`)**\n   - **Interactive Selection Cards**: Renders today\'s recommended workouts displaying target sets, repetitions, target muscles, and recommended intervals.\n   - **Weekly stats row**: Dynamically computes active sessions completed, total sets completed, and average workout goals completion percentage directly from state.\n   - **Real-Time AI Chat**: Includes a fast-response coach console at the top prompting feedback, form cues, or nutritional tips, marked by a crimson left border.\n\n3. **Goal-Based Training Hubs (`/train`)**\n   - Segmented goal selectors: **STRENGTH** (Pure raw muscle building), **FAT LOSS / HIIT** (High calorie exhaustion), and **ATHLETIC SPEED** (Explosive plyometrics).\n   - Instant filtering loads relevant lists of 5 specialized exercises for a total of 15 fully-guided routines.\n\n4. **Collapsible Accordion Program Planner (`/program`)**\n   - Collapsible day cards from Monday to Sunday representing the 8-Week Elite Hybrid routine.\n   - **Auto-Expansion Priority**: Automatically detects the current calendar day and begins expanded, giving users direct focus-points immediately upon login.\n\n5. **Athlete Bio & Configuration (`/profile`)**\n   - Visual status bar tracking gained XP toward Level 8 (with interactive gamification that awards **+100 XP** and leveling milestones on finishing sets).\n   - Tappable goal selectors and custom setting switches (Rest alert sounds, video auto-plays, and notification reminders) storing values persistently in `localStorage`.\n\n6. **Sliding Exercise Detail Panel**\n   - Interactive bottom modal featuring embedded instructional **YouTube demonstration videos** for form guides.\n   - **Set completion tracker**: Individually clickable bubbles that log each finished set on tap and update overall progress levels immediately.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\247\240 Server-Side AI Coaching Engine\n\n- Implemented a custom Express secure backend routing through `/api/trainer` with `@google/genai` on `gemini-3.5-flash`.\n- **Secret Protection**: Lazy-loaded the personal key server-side from `process.env.GEMINI_API_KEY`, keeping your access credentials fully invisible to client browsers.\n- **Graceful Failures**: If your API key has not yet been defined in the Settings secrets array, the AI coach falls back gracefully, providing top-tier preloaded athletic guidelines and a simple prompt teaching how to activate live responses in a single step!\n"
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
