    user_response: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\\\"en\\\"><head><meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\"><style>body{margin:0;padding:0;overflow:hidden;background-color:#0f0f0f;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\',Arial,sans-serif;color:#ffffff;height:768px;width:1024px}.bebas{font-family:\'Arial Black\',Gadget,sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px}.accent-glow{box-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(226,75,74,0.4)}.red-gradient{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e24b4a 0%,#992121 100%)}.glass-card{background:rgba(26,26,26,0.8);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border-radius:12px}.sidebar-item-active{background:rgba(226,75,74,0.1);color:#e24b4a;border-right:3px solid #e24b4a}.dot{height:8px;width:8px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:4px}.dot-active{background-color:#e24b4a;box-shadow:0 0 5px #e24b4a}.dot-inactive{background-color:#333}</style></head><body><div class=\\\"flex h-screen w-full bg-[#0f0f0f]\\\"><aside class=\\\"w-64 border-r border-white/5 flex flex-col\\\"><div class=\\\"p-8\\\"><h1 class=\\\"bebas text-2xl text-[#e24b4a] italic\\\">Fitness World</h1><p class=\\\"text-[10px] opacity-40 -mt-1 tracking-widest\\\">AI-POWERED PERFORMANCE</p></div><nav class=\\\"flex-1 mt-4\\\"><div class=\\\"px-4 mb-2\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest px-4 mb-4\\\">Main Menu</p><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"sidebar-item-active flex items-center px-4 py-3 rounded-lg mb-1\\\"><span class=\\\"mr-3\\\">\342\212\236</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Dashboard</span></a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors mb-1\\\"><span class=\\\"mr-3\\\">\342\232\241</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Training</span></a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors mb-1\\\"><span class=\\\"mr-3\\\">\360\237\223\205</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Programs</span></a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors mb-1\\\"><span class=\\\"mr-3\\\">\360\237\221\244</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Profile</span></a></div></nav><div class=\\\"p-6 mt-auto border-t border-white/5\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-3\\\"><div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center bebas border border-[#e24b4a]\\\">FW</div><div><p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">Warrior #802</p><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40\\\">Level 7 \342\200\224 Intermediate</p></div></div></div></aside><main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col relative\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#e24b4a]/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] -z-10\\\"></div><header class=\\\"h-20 flex items-center justify-between px-10 border-b border-white/5\\\"><h2 class=\\\"bebas text-3xl\\\">Ready to Grind?</h2><div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-6\\\"><div class=\\\"text-right\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase\\\">Monday, Oct 23</p><p class=\\\"text-sm font-bold tracking-tight\\\">WEEK 4: HYPERTROPHY</p></div><div class=\\\"w-px h-8 bg-white/10\\\"></div><div class=\\\"text-right\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase\\\">Status</p><p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#e24b4a] font-bold\\\">TRAINING LIVE</p></div></div></header><div class=\\\"flex-1 p-10 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8\\\"><div class=\\\"col-span-8 space-y-8\\\"><div class=\\\"glass-card p-6 border-l-4 border-l-[#e24b4a]\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-2\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[#e24b4a] text-lg\\\">\342\234\246</span><h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#e24b4a]\\\">AI Coaching Insight</h3></div><span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-white/5 px-2 py-1 rounded\\\">JUST NOW</span></div><p class=\\\"text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed\\\">\\\"Based on your squat form yesterday, try to engage your core more today. You\'re hitting 85% of your max volume. Keep the intensity high for the Romanian Deadlifts!\\\"</p></div><section><div><h3 class=\\\"bebas text-xl mb-4 flex items-center\\\">Today\'s Routine <span class=\\\"ml-4 h-px flex-1 bg-white/5\\\"></span></h3><div class=\\\"grid gap-3\\\"><div class=\\\"glass-card p-4 flex items-center justify-between\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-4\\\"><div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 rounded bg-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl\\\">\360\237\217\213\357\270\217</div><div><p class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Barbell Back Squat</p><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Quads \342\200\242 Heavy Power</p></div></div><div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-12\\\"><div class=\\\"text-center\\\"><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/40\\\">SETS \303\227 REPS</p><p class=\\\"font-bold bebas\\\">5 \303\227 5</p></div><div class=\\\"text-center\\\"><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/40\\\">PROGRESS</p><div class=\\\"flex mt-1\\\"><span class=\\\"dot dot-active\\\"></span><span class=\\\"dot dot-active\\\"></span><span class=\\\"dot dot-active\\\"></span><span class=\\\"dot dot-inactive\\\"></span><span class=\\\"dot dot-inactive\\\"></span></div></div><button class=\\\"p-2 bg-white/5 hover:bg-[#e24b4a] transition-all rounded text-xs\\\">DETAILS</button></div></div><div class=\\\"glass-card p-4 flex items-center justify-between opacity-80\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-4\\\"><div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 rounded bg-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl\\\">\360\237\246\265</div><div><p class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Romanian Deadlift</p><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Hamstrings \342\200\242 Controlled</p></div></div><div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-12\\\"><div class=\\\"text-center\\\"><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/40\\\">SETS \303\227 REPS</p><p class=\\\"font-bold bebas\\\">4 \303\227 12</p></div><div class=\\\"text-center\\\"><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/40\\\">PROGRESS</p><div class=\\\"flex mt-1\\\"><span class=\\\"dot dot-inactive\\\"></span><span class=\\\"dot dot-inactive\\\"></span><span class=\\\"dot dot-inactive\\\"></span><span class=\\\"dot dot-inactive\\\"></span></div></div><button class=\\\"p-2 bg-white/5 rounded text-xs\\\">DETAILS</button></div></div></div></div></section></div><div class=\\\"col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-6\\\"><div class=\\\"glass-card p-6 flex flex-col justify-between h-48\\\"><p class=\\\"bebas text-sm text-white/60\\\">XP Progress</p><div class=\\\"flex items-end justify-between\\\"><h4 class=\\\"bebas text-5xl\\\">1360</h4><p class=\\\"text-xs text-white/40 mb-1\\\">/ 2000 XP</p></div><div class=\\\"w-full h-2 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full overflow-hidden mt-4\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full red-gradient accent-glow w-[68%]\\\"></div></div></div><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\"><div class=\\\"glass-card p-4 text-center\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase mb-1\\\">Streak</p><p class=\\\"bebas text-2xl\\\">21</p><p class=\\\"text-[9px] text-[#e24b4a] uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Days Hot</p></div><div class=\\\"glass-card p-4 text-center\\\"><p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase mb-1\\\">Workouts</p><p class=\\\"bebas text-2xl\\\">34</p><p class=\\\"text-[9px] text-white/20 uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Total</p></div></div><div class=\\\"glass-card p-6 flex-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1a1a1a] to-[#0f0f0f]\\\"><h4 class=\\\"bebas text-sm mb-4\\\">Weekly Volume</h4><div class=\\\"flex items-end justify-between h-32 px-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-8 bg-[#e24b4a]/20 h-16 rounded-t\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-8 bg-[#e24b4a]/40 h-24 rounded-t\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-8 bg-[#e24b4a]/60 h-20 rounded-t\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-8 bg-[#e24b4a] accent-glow h-28 rounded-t\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-8 bg-neutral-800 h-10 rounded-t\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-8 bg-neutral-800 h-8 rounded-t\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-8 bg-neutral-800 h-12 rounded-t\\\"></div></div><div class=\\\"flex justify-between mt-2 text-[8px] text-white/30 bebas px-2\\\"><p>MON</p><p>TUE</p><p>WED</p><p>THU</p><p>FRI</p><p>SAT</p><p>SUN</p></div></div></div></div></main></div></body></html>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\\\"en\\\"><head><meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\"><style>body{margin:0;padding:0;overflow:hidden;background-color:#0f0f0f;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\',Arial,sans-serif;color:#ffffff;height:768px;width:1024px}.bebas{font-family:\'Arial Black\',Gadget,sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px}.accent-glow{box-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(226,75,74,0.4)}.red-gradient{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e24b4a 0%,#992121 100%)}.glass-card{background:rgba(26,26,26,0.8);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border:1px solid rgba(255,2