  planner_response {
    modified_response: "I have successfully designed and integrated the fully customizable training splits based on the user\'s focus, maintaining absolute alignment and real-time state synchronization across all views:\n\n- **Dynamic Split Integration**: Replaced the static weekly schedule with five bespoke, elite 7-day programs designed for specific sports paradigms:\n  - **Beginners**: Light conditioning and mastering basic joint biomechanics.\n  - **Weight Loss**: High-intensity metabolic circuits and caloric deficit conditioning.\n  - **Bodybuilder**: Continuous-tension muscle isolating hypertrophy volumes.\n  - **Powerlifter**: Neuromuscular explosive strength with Squats, Bench Presses, and Conventional Deadlifts.\n  - **Athletic Speed**: Force rate mechanics, triple-extensions, agility cones, and plyometric reactive jumps.\n- **Interconnective Split Chooser**: Fabricated a luxurious and responsive tab panel inside the **8-Week Program View**, allowing the user to hot-swap active programs. Switching splits instantly updates calculations, day descriptions, and modifies their core profile\'s focus key so that global dashboard metrics sync seamlessly.\n- **Visual Aesthetic Refinement**: Elevated select containers with interactive glowing bounds and custom red gradient tags to accentuate active choices with smooth interface feedback."
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
